Revision history for Perl extension File::Butler.

3.00  16-Jan-2002
        - Overall code clean-up.
        - Added OO interface.
        - Modified write(), append(), and prepend() to accept scalar
          input, instead of restricting input to arrays.

2.00  10-Jul-2001
        - after numerous revisions, first public release

1.00  01-Jul-2000
        - original version, available in limited release
